2b","tid":524862,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d7df4db74e03a088318271ea29931fb7b8bfe5","tid":524862,"uid":37708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"嘉倩bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b2d15b54050a34990b2273da0fac22121ff13b","tid":524862,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"條友唔知講真定假<br />\n有冇閃卡先"},{"pid":"93255009d02100dc9f9c51be566ae6f74fd377e1","tid":524862,"uid":61271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"好，改撐陳嘉倩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f63b32d5754cde84f36f699d446b11664401e3c","tid":524862,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"【女神輸曬】陳嘉倩俾前度陳志遠爆 擺明做小三<br />\n<br />\n前大台新聞主播女神，俾網民封為「嘉倩BB」嘅陳嘉倩，因為俾人影到同圈外男友陳志遠拍拖，一段三角關係被揭，屬正印嘅大台藝員朱婉禎鬧佢爭仔，擺明做小三。<br />\n<br />\n事件發展落去，陳嘉倩唔認小三身份，繼而報警話受到滋擾，點知三角關係高潮係，食兩家劈腿男陳志遠企出嚟認係賤男外，亦力証陳嘉倩明知佢有女友，都照舂個頭埋嚟做小三，佢接受訪問時話溝陳嘉倩時，已表明有正印朱婉禎存在，但佢都選擇同佢一齊，仲話佢先係俾人電話滋擾，兼夾座駕俾人損毀，即係受害嗰一個。<br />\n<br />\n做小三，基本上預咗兩敗俱傷嘅下場，仲要撞正個劈腿衰咗擺你上枱嘅男人，呢舖真係輸到底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180116/568159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180116%2F568159&d=jv5VVIV7ClBSI%2BGCvZSj9TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f5b982fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180116%2F568159&h=7061f44b\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180116/568159</a>"},{"pid":"3d00ddf8cc7c82fc8a3815f3a97fa2f1c708f038","tid":52